/// All relationships ship inactive by default. Activate selectively in
/// Power BI Desktop after refreshing once and confirming uniqueness on the
/// dim side (DimRoute/DimStop have provider_id + dataset_version_id +
/// natural-key composite uniqueness; with a single active dataset version
/// the natural-key relationship holds in practice). Toggle via
/// Model view → Relationship → Active checkbox.

